oken property\">attributes</span><span class=\"token operator\">-></span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string single-quoted-string\">'node'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-></span><span class=\"token function\">bundle</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<div><em>load node</em></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"php\"><pre class=\"language-php\"><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token comment\">// Drupal 7</span>\n<span class=\"token variable\">$nid</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">123</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token variable\">$node</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">node_load</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$nid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Drupal 8</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Drupal<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>node<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Entity<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Node</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token variable\">$nid</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">123</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token variable\">$node</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name static-context\">Node</span><span class=\"token operator\">::</span><span class=\"token function\">load</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$nid</span><span c